\paragraph{Precision, Recall and F-measure:}
Besides using FRR, FAR and DER to evaluate the performance of MDD, other metrics such
as precision, recall and F-measure are also widely used as the performance measures for mispronunciation detection. These metrics are defined as follows:

\begin{equation}
Precision = \frac{TR}{TR + FR}
\end{equation}

\begin{equation}
Recall = \frac{TR}{TR + FA} = 1 - FAR
\end{equation}

\begin{equation}
F-measure = 2 \cdot \frac{Precision \cdot Recall}{Precision + Recall}
\end{equation}


